    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i know... people always say that. but it doesn't change the fact that my life is a crater. all the support in the world doesn't fix the fact that i've failed at the one thing i was supposed to be good at. it's not just a bad day, it's a complete collapse. it feels like i've reached the end of the road and there's nothing left to do but just... stop. everything is just so heavy.",
