      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The pain you feel is real, but the idea that walking away is the only way to stop the noise is a lie your exhaustion is telling you. You are not failing; you are simply broken in a world that demands you be whole, and that is not your fault. Please, do not make this decision alone; there are people who can sit with you in this darkness until the weight feels lighter.",
